, "id": "2_1710148180.954230", "card_id": "Q_648014007", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "今年首批储蓄国债发行首日遭抢购，有银行额度开售半个小时售罄，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2024 年第一期、第二期储蓄国债（凭证式）于 3 月 10 日正式发售。根据财政部官网消息，本次国债最大发行总额为 300 亿元。其中，第一期期限为 3 年，票面年利率 2.38%；第二期期限为 5 年，票面年利率 2.5%。 投资者购买的储蓄国债（凭证式）从购买之日开始计息，到期一次还本付息，不计复利，逾期兑付不加计利息。按照目前的利率计算，市民如果购买本次发行的 10 万元 3 年期和 10 万元 5 年期储蓄国债，到期后累计收益分别为 7140 元、 12500 元。 据中国证券报报道，尽管新一期储蓄国债利率较前一期有所下行，但依旧受到投资者追捧。不少银行营业网点的储蓄国债开售不到半个小时，就已售罄。「半小时，售罄！」有银行网点人均出手 20 万，不少人排队也没买到！客户经理：这种产品一般要靠抢 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c1ad2f28230851d9c337541683b76f95_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "294 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/648014007"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItIWyl9jV/pg0EAMaCTEwNjI4MDI5OSDU+bmvBjAAOExAAnIJNjQ4MDE0MDA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1710148180.955871", "card_id": "Q_293079013", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 92}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何直观的感受葛立恒数？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8391516138397a4197f276fa9cab4180_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "232 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/293079013"}}, "a